org.atlanmod.commons

Class LazyBoolean

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.atlanmod.commons.LazyBoolean

  • @ParametersAreNonnullByDefault
public final class LazyBoolean
extends Object
    An object that automatically loads a boolean by using a BooleanSupplier during the first call to getAsBoolean().
